    {
      "_id": "wjYRbuwLbzXVEPRT",
      "name": "Mocking Word",
      "type": "feat",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em><strong></strong> </em>The nilbog targets one creature it can see within 60 feet of it. The target must succeed on a [[/save wis 12 format=long]] or take [[/damage 2d4 type=psychic average=true]] damage and have disadvantage on its next attack roll before the end of its next turn.</p>\n</section>\nThe [[lookup @name]] uses [[lookup @item.name]] and a save is required.\n</div>",
          "chat": ""
